title: TNF Recap;  Week 5 Preview
itunes:title: TNF Recap;  Week 5 Preview
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, & Gregg Rosenthal take you through all week 5 games for the upcoming weekend. Dan also is surrounded by two Patriots fans for the Thursday night recap where the heroes fill you in on where the Tampa Bay Buccaneers came up short. Everything you need to know about Week 5 is here.
